title: Masters of Photography (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
pdf / English / 192 pag / 1958 / ISBN-10: 1135787328 / 21 MB

Photographers surveyed : David Octavius Hill and Robert Adamson ; Albert Sands Southworth and Josiah Johnson Hawes ; Nadar ; Alexander Gardner and Timothy H. O'Sullivan ; Julia Margaret Cameron ; Peter Henry Emerson ; Alfred Stieglitz ; Edward Steichen ; Euge`ne Atget ; Paul Strand ; Edward Weston ; Erich Salomon ; Dorothea Lange ; Walker Evans ; Henri Cartier-Bresson ; Ansel Adams. Includes short biographies of each photographer surveyed, and numerous examples of their photographs.
